column5: So what are some of the stuff everyone will be looking forward to?>
The Abu Garcia rods, Patriarch spinning, and possibly the sufix/gore tex braided line!
quantum smoke PT baitcating reels, new koppers live target baits, strike king baits. to name just a few lol
New season of Getting School'd to see what is new out there I gues with the cheap prices on flights it might be worth the plane ride from Detroit one of these years to go check it out.

G Loomis NRX line of rods. Amazing. Cant wait till they are available, Shimano's Curado 50 reel and their new Slatwater gear. IMA baits, Koppers, Ko-Man-Chi Docter Spinnerbaits. Very interesting stuff this year for sure. I'm still reading through all the stuff.
